scopecontent.p:
The collection has been organized into series which reflect both Menger's style of work
            and his major areas of research. The series include: research notebooks; manuscripts and
            notes on economic principles, money, and methodology; teaching materials;
            correspondence; biographical and personal materials; related family materials;
            miscellany; and printed matter.

